* ''Bondarzewia guaitecasensis''
* [[圆刺孢多孔菌|圆刺孢多孔菌]] ''Bondarzewia mesenterica''
* [[圆瘤孢多孔菌|圆瘤孢多孔菌]] ''Bondarzewia montana'' (Quél.) Singer (≡ ''Polyporus montanus'' (Quél.) Ferry)，圆孢地花
* [[罗汉松刺孢多孔菌|罗汉松刺孢多孔菌]] ''Bondarzewia podocarpi''
* [[西藏刺孢多孔菌|西藏刺孢多孔菌]] ''Bondarzewia tibetica''
* ''Bondarzewia zonata''

